  "text": "A qualitative, interview-based, study was designed. The study population of interest was people who had purchased a home BP monitor for their own use. Those who had been provided with a monitor through their healthcare provider (e.g. the UK National Health Service -NHS) were thus excluded. We then purposefully selected participants to provide maximum variation [CITATION_1] in relation to the health condition that triggered the device purchase.",
